dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Ethan Sanders. May I have your name please?
Nice to meet you, Donna! How can I assist you today? Could you provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is six seven eight nine.
Thank you, Donna. Additionally, I'll need your date of birth to access your account. What is your date of birth?
My date of birth is zero four two five one nine seven eight.
Thank you for providing that information, Donna. I will now look up your account details. Is there anything specific you would like to inquire about today?
Yes, I would like to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, I can assist you with that. Let's review the details of your new vehicle. Once I have the necessary information, we can proceed with the addition to your policy.
Thank you for your time, Donna. If you have any further questions, please feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
